    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some fading paint on the roof, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and carpets. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but it will eventually need work on the suspension and a tune-up to address a slightly hesitant idle. It is a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a bit of character and some upcoming DIY projects.",
