    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This car is in great shape and has clearly been well-loved, offering a smooth ride and a clean, attractive look both inside and out. It\u2019s a reliable performer that\u2019s ready for many more miles of adventure, making it the perfect choice for someone who wants a high-quality vehicle without the brand-new price tag. Honest, solid, and ready for a new home!",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
